column1: Uchi////Fried milk - 100000000/10 I honestly don't even have any words to describe this dessert because it's probably the best thing I've ever put in my mouth
column2: EVERRRRRRR. Seriously this dessert was PHENOMENAL and full of so many different textures. If I had to choose a dessert for my last meal on earth
column3: this would hands down be the one.
